item.title: Courier Logo
item.description: I designed this courier logo first as a personal project. At first it was going to be a full fledged digital illustration, but after finishing the head I decided to create as a mock up logo. Geometric, Clean and Minimal I decided to keep a clean minimal style for this project and based it all on basic shapes. Vector Illustration in Adobe Illustrator I used adobe illustrator to create this logo, staring off with a circle, triangle and rectangle for the head, and a semi circle for the head.
